Package com.kissair.util

This package contains various utility classes which could not be classified to belong directly to other packages.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FlightCentreDecoder
    The class for decoding messages received from the FlightCentre clients.
    FlightCentreEncoder
    The class for encoding messages sent via the FlightCentre web-socket.
    FormatHelper
    The FormatHelper class, which contains methods for proper formatting of Flight's fields data.
    HibernateUtil
    The HibernateUtil class provided on the Hibernate documentation page.
    Message
    This class encapsulates messages transmitted between the FlightCentre server endpoint and its clients.

Package com.kissair.util Description

This package contains various utility classes which could not be classified to belong directly to other packages. These classes mainly provide additional functionality.
